      <title>南非最大的政党在四月之前寻求预算妥协</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/south-africa-s-anc-da-in-talks-to-end-budget-impasse</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非的两个最大政党正在举行一系列谈判，以解决国家预算上的僵局，这对该国统治联盟的稳定构成了最大的威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/south-africa-s-anc-da-in-talks-to-end-budget-impasse</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 06:04:25 GMT</pubDate>
