    <item>
      <title>波兰在投票前提出防御网络攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/poland-election-authorities-bolster-online-defenses-against-cyberattacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据副总理Gawkowski说，波兰正在努力支持在线安全并与社交媒体平台进行交谈，以期在总统大选之前会增加网络攻击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/poland-election-authorities-bolster-online-defenses-against-cyberattacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其的埃尔多安（Erdogan）在四月寻求白宫与特朗普会面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/turkey-s-erdogan-seeks-white-house-meeting-with-trump-in-april</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据熟悉此事的土耳其官员说，土耳其总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安（Recep Tayyip Erdogan）正在努力确保与唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）在白宫举行会议，这可能是在4月底之前的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/turkey-s-erdogan-seeks-white-house-meeting-with-trump-in-april</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国立法者对地标支出法案投票：值得关注的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/german-lawmakers-vote-on-landmark-spending-bill-what-to-watch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国立法者将在周二的一项法案上投票，该法案将在债务资助的国防和基础设施支出中释放数千亿欧元，并预示着在欧洲最大的经济体中更广泛的财政政策的枢纽。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/german-lawmakers-vote-on-landmark-spending-bill-what-to-watch</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国计划削减游客的无签证住宿至30天</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/thailand-mulls-cutting-tourists-visa-free-stay-to-30-days</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据旅游业和体育部长Sorawong Thienthong的说法，泰国计划使外国游客能够在没有签证的情况下停留的天数减少到30天，因为东南亚国家打击旅行者，利用豁免来从事非法业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/thailand-mulls-cutting-tourists-visa-free-stay-to-30-days</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 01:54:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
